# Milestone Deep Dive Projection

## Purpose

This projection defines how an epic’s milestones should be transformed into durable implementation-planning specifications.

It exists to support:

- epic-preserving milestone expansion
- capability-stage refinement
- architecture-preserving planning
- dependency-fidelity preservation
- boundary definition
- validation strategy creation
- completion evidence definition
- execution-readiness preparation
- traceable milestone planning

It is a projection of the Core North-Star, not an epic, milestone spec, execution prompt, repository audit, roadmap artifact, or implementation plan.

## Authority Boundary

- The Core North-Star remains the source of authority.
- This projection is a task-specific planning view of the Core North-Star.
- This projection defines how GenerateMilestoneDeepDivesForEpic should create milestone planning specifications.
- This projection does not include selected epic content.
- This projection does not include repository state.
- This projection does not create milestone deep dives.
- This projection does not generate implementation tasks.
- This projection does not create execution prompts.
- This projection does not modify roadmap, epic, or projection content.

