| ID | Capability-Stage Rule | Meaning | Planning Implication |
|---|---|---|---|

Examples:

- milestone outcome states what becomes true
- milestone represents one coherent capability stage
- milestone should not be a task bucket
- milestone should enable downstream capability stages
- final milestone should prove epic-level success

## Planning Specification Rules

Define what each milestone deep dive should contain.

| ID | Spec Element | Required Purpose | Quality Rule |
|---|---|---|---|

