| ID | Boundary Rule | Meaning | Required Behavior |
|---|---|---|---|

Include rules for:

- what the milestone owns
- what the milestone excludes
- what is deferred to later milestones
- what is inherited from earlier milestones
- what must not leak into this milestone
- how to prevent duplicate ownership

