- Epic Realignment Required
- Epic Reimagination Required
- Human Clarification Required
- Insufficient Milestone Structure
- Projection Conflict
- Different Prompt Required

Examples:

- selected epic lacks milestone roadmap
- milestone ordering is contradictory
- milestone dependencies are unclear
- milestone completion signals are missing
- expansion would require redesigning the epic
- architecture is too underspecified to plan safely
- acceptance criteria cannot be mapped to milestones
- milestone boundaries overlap irreconcilably

