- capability stage must trace to epic desired capability
- constraints must trace to epic or projection
- validation strategy must trace to acceptance criteria
- completion evidence must trace to milestone outcome
- deferred work must trace to later milestone or non-goal
- final milestone must trace to epic success conditions

